### Check if user can apply to an event
GET http://localhost:8000/applications/check-eligibility?user_id=1&event_id=1


### Create a new application (volunteer applies to event)
POST http://localhost:8000/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 1,
  "event_id": 1
}

### Create another application
POST http://localhost:8000/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 2,
  "event_id": 1
}

### Test application limit - try to apply to same event twice
POST http://localhost:8000/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 1,
  "event_id": 1
}

### Test applying to closed event
POST http://localhost:8000/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": 3,
  "event_id": 5
}

### Test application with non-existent user
POST http://localhost:8000/applications
