### Update application status
PUT http://localhost:8000/applications/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "accepted"
}

### Test invalid status update
PUT http://localhost:8000/applications/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "invalid_status"
}

### Accept an application (specific endpoint)
POST http://localhost:8000/applications/1/accept

### Reject an application
POST http://localhost:8000/applications/2/reject

### Mark application as completed (volunteer attended)
POST http://localhost:8000/applications/1/complete

### Mark application as no-show (volunteer didn't attend)
POST http://localhost:8000/applications/3/no-show

### Delete an application
DELETE http://localhost:8000/applications/1
